{"tid":37862,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[懶有品味]切牛扒教學","createTime":"2016-12-13T14:44:28.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T15:18:02.000Z","uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c2415c2a05bf1bc4b5793f44d74ba9ff008e3b03","tid":37862,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T14:44:28.000Z","msg":"我睇post見到有巴打話餐廳刀唔夠利 又或者肉太多筋 切極都切唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實有用開鋸既朋友就知道，切肉同鋸木係同一道理。<br />\n<br />\n第一，揸刀係用主手。你自己都話牛扒多筋，仲用副手咪即係玩自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二，切扒動作係由上而下，一下接住一下。千其唔好上下上下狂切，切唔到之餘仲好失儀態。<br />\n牛扒刀鋸齒既設計係順切，你拖返上去係切唔到任何野。動作係向下拖，返原位，向下拖。動作慢慢黎就已經可以切開份扒。<br />\n跟住咁做，就算幾厚既扒三五下就會切開。<br />\n<br />\n有其它西餐心得既巴絲一齊分享下。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8072708b49c3db9234a0abe1262a7b6399d3ad3","tid":37862,"uid":50286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T14:44:56.000Z","msg":"好勁呀"},{"pid":"c7959e941493b4aaf394f8edf83cff5d01a58ca2","tid":37862,"uid":20448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:07:43.000Z","msg":"切賓周呢<br />\n海綿體肉質可以點先一刀到尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n純學術交流"},{"pid":"1f605143213ec46981928fb386e40e661979c9ce","tid":37862,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:09:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>切賓周呢<br />\n海綿體肉質可以點先一刀到尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n純學術交流</blockquote><br />\n切賓周梗係開邊蒜蓉蒸啦"},{"pid":"492fdc1caa4b56b71a4f43d46e77ad3725ba17f8","tid":37862,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:11:47.000Z","msg":"睇cony個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8475e3f4243c4c82486d0b6f3e1c3f730522004","tid":37862,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:12:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇cony個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊個係cony?"},{"pid":"5bb1e1dc08d13858d6068c563d55092d0b03e8e5","tid":37862,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:18:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇cony個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊個係cony?</blockquote><br />\n個絲打話d牛扒切唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}